This paper is about optimizing large-scale machine learning applications, which is a topic that falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the use of distributed computing and high-performance computing techniques, which could fall under the categories of distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), software engineering (cs.SE), and databases (cs.DB).
